<h1>RSS+</h1>

RSS+ allows you to subscribe to the content linked to by a website - even if that website doesn't have an RSS feed. To begin, enter the URL of the site you want to subscribe to in the box below.

<form name="urlform" action="http://www.mydomain.com/myformhandler.cgi" method="POST">
<div align="center">
<br><br>
<input type="text" size="25" value="Enter your name here!">
<br><input type="submit" value="Send me your name!"><br>
</div>
</form>
